      "body": "**Actionable comments posted: 1**\n\n<details>\n<summary>\ud83e\uddf9 Nitpick comments (2)</summary><blockquote>\n\n<details>\n<summary>src/oci/builder.rs (1)</summary><blockquote>\n\n`244-258`: _\ud83d\udd12 Security & Privacy_ | _\ud83d\udd35 Trivial_ | _\u26a1 Quick win_\n\n**Consider warning when copying host paths, mirroring the existing `[env]` secrets warning.**\n\n`build_image_config` already warns when baking `[env]` values into the image because they're visible via `docker/skopeo inspect`. Host paths copied via `--copy`/`[[oci.copy]]` carry the same risk (e.g. an accidentally-included `.env`, `.git`, or SSH key inside a copied directory) but get no equivalent notice.\n\n<details>\n<summary>\ud83d\udee1\ufe0f Suggested addition</summary>\n\n```diff\n         for copy in copies {\n             copy.validate().map_err(eyre::Report::msg)?;\n+            info!(\n+                \"mise oci build: copying host path {} into the image at {} \u2014 \\\n+                 review its contents for secrets/credentials before sharing the image\",\n+                copy.host.display(),\n+                copy.image\n+            );\n             let blob = layer::build_layer_from_path(&copy.host, &copy.image, owner).wrap_err_with(\n```\n</details>\n\n<details>\n<summary>\ud83e\udd16 Prompt for AI Agents</summary>\n\n```\nVerify each finding against current code. Fix only still-valid issues, skip the\nrest with a brief reason, keep changes minimal, and validate.\n\nIn `@src/oci/bui…12677 tokens truncated…SC_CONTAINER_REGISTRY: nscr.io/bha599b0o6716\ntest-ci\tUNKNOWN STEP\t2026-07-12T01:03:52.8107300Z ##[endgroup]\ntest-ci\tUNKNOWN STEP\t2026-07-12T01:03:52.8137457Z lint failed or was skipped\ntest-ci\tUNKNOWN STEP\t2026-07-12T01:03:52.8147301Z ##[error]Process completed with exit code 1.\ntest-ci\tUNKNOWN STEP\t2026-07-12T01:03:52.8211961Z Cleaning up orphan processes\ntest-ci\tUNKNOWN STEP\t2026-07-12T01:03:52.8249427Z Terminate orphan process: pid (191) (gh